<html lang="en">

<body>
    <div class="container" id="pageCenterID">
        <div class="row" id="centerContentID" style="margin-bottom:0em;">
            <h2 style="color:#632D63;">&nbsp;Cancer Centers</h2>
            <hr style="margin-bottom:0em;" />
            <ul class="breadcrumb" id="centerContentID" style="float:left;">
                <li><a href="home" id="home">@Html.ActionLink("Home", "Index", "Home")</a> <span aria-hidden="true" class="glyphicon glyphicon-circle-arrow-right"></span></li>
                <li class="active grayFont">Cancer Centers</li>          
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:0em;">
            <div class="col-sm-4" style="text-justify:inter-word;">
                <br />

                <div accesskey="s" class="btn btn-default btn-sm" style="width:280px; border-color:#D8CAD8; float:left;">
                    <a href="@Url.Action("CCList", "Center")" class="tip-bottom tooltipColor" data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="Click here to go to the Cancer Centers List"><strong>69 NCI-Designated Cancer Centers</strong></a>
</div>
                <div class="inbar" style="width:280px;border-color:#D8CAD8;">
                    <ul>
                        <li><div class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">49</div>&nbsp;Comprehensive</li>
                        <li><div class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">13</div>&nbsp;Clinical</li>
                        <li><div class="btn btn-success btn-sm">07</div>&nbsp;Basic</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div style="clear:both"></div>
                </div>
                <br />

                <p>NCI-designated Cancer Centers are characterized by scientific excellence and the capability to integrate a diversity of research approaches to focus on the problem of cancer.</p>
                <p>They play a vital role in advancing towards our goal of reducing morbidity and mortality from cancer.</p>
                <br />
                <a href="~/DT/DT">Cancer Centers Benchmark Data</a>         
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <br />
                <img src="~/images/CCMap69.jpg" alt="NCI-designated Cancer Centers Map" style="float:left;border-color:#D8CAD8; width:580px; height:360px;" />
            </div>
        </div> <!--end of row-->
         
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-4" style="text-justify:inter-word;">
                <h5><strong>Cancer Centers List</strong></h5>
                <p>A comprehensive directory with contact information for all our cancer centers.</p>
                <a href="~/Center/CCList"> Find a cancer center &raquo;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4" style="text-justify:inter-word;">
                <h5><strong>Research Programs</strong></h5>
                <p>Research programs promote collaborative research between basic laboratory, clinical, and population sciences.</p>
                <a href="~/Documents/researchprogramsreported2014-508c.pdf" target="_blank"> Find a research program &raquo;</a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4" style="text-justify:inter-word;">
                <h5><strong>Shared Resources</strong></h5>
                <p>Shared resources provide researchers access to cutting edge technologies and services that promote scientific interaction and productivity.</p>
                <a href="~/Center/SharedResource"> Find a shared resource &raquo;</a>
            </div>
        </div> <!--end of row -->
    </div>
</body>
</html>